Bad Bunny and BLACKPINK's Lisa made history, with Bad Bunny as the first non-English-language act to take out the Artist of the Year award, and Lisa as the first solo K-Pop artist to win a VMA by winning the Best K-Pop award. Keep it here for all the wins and excitement from the night.
